    • Method Detail

      • buildSuggestion

        public void buildSuggestion(int maxSize)
        This method calls the recursiveMerge with selfFunc to create a placeholder SuggestionTrie.Node storing a Map of prefix to document frequency. mergeFunc maps the list storing descendants' nodes and 1 placeholder node from selfFunc, and data/node of this trie, to a new SuggestionTrie.Node with document frequency being the same as the data/node of this trie, with Map<String, Integer> storing top maxSize amount of Map.Entry(word, document frequency of the word) with respect to the document frequency of the word, where the words in the Map are from either descendants or this trie.
        Parameters:
        maxSize - max suggestions size stored in SuggestionTrie.Node
